{
  "stem": "1061.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was some barracks put in or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or maybe there were barracks there before, but I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because this was not anymore in the town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- the community in which I lived had this industrial town and a bedroom town, you see?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The bedroom town where everybody lived was called Wierzbnik.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the big town, the industrial part where the factory was, was Starachowice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was really combined and named Starachowice, but everybody lived in the bedroom town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, this Strzelnica camp was very near the factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have never heard of it, I've never seen it, and I found myself completely alone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cried and I was petrified.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think the terror-- the real terror that gripped me in all my war-- war experiences, that was that point.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was of the greatest terror in my life because I was really alone, totally alone, for the first time in my life.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was only thanks to the people around me who comforted me, who-- who hugged me, who held me by my hand, and-- and don't cry, and your mother will come soon, and all this.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was totally stricken with horror, with-- with fear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, I have experienced fear after this point, too, you know, with the [? write-through. ?] After all, the war was already on for two years.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I have experienced enough fear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But nothing like that excruciating pain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, after everything settled down, I discovered that my father found himself in the same camp where I was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we also found out that there was another camp established around the area in a place called Majowka.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
